file.name: filestorage-component.openapi.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: File Storage Component
  description: Component
  version: 1.0.0

paths: {}

components:
  schemas:
    MultipleBucket:
      type: object
      properties:
        total:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          minimum: 0
        buckets:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Bucket'
      required:
        - total
        - buckets
    SingleBucket:
      type: object
      properties:
        bucket:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Bucket'
      required:
        - bucket
    Bucket:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        resource_owner_id:
          type: string
        created_at:
          type: string
        created_by:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreatedBy'
        updated_at:
          type: string
        updated_by:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/UpdatedBy'
        name:
          type: string
        files:
          type: object
          properties:
            total_count:
              type: string
            total_size:
              type: string
      required:
        - id
        - resource_owner_id
        - name
    BucketRequest:
      type: object
      properties:
        resource_owner_id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
        name:
          type: string
      required:
        - name
        - resource_owner_id
    BucketEditBody:
      type: object
      properties:
        dest_bucket_id:
          type: string
        parent_node_id:
          type: string
    BucketName:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
      required:
        - name
    NodeName:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
      required:
        - name

    MultipleNode:
      type: object
      properties:
        total:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        nodes:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Node'
      required:
        - total
        - nodes
    SingleNode:
      type: object
      properties:
        node:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Node'
      required:
        - node
    Node:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        created_at:
          type: string
        created_by:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreatedBy'
        updated_at:
          type: string
        updated_by:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/UpdatedBy'
        name:
          type: string
        parent_node_id:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        key:
          type: string
        is_directory:
          type: boolean
        file:
          type: object
          properties:
            size:
              type: string
            checksum:
              type: string
      required:
        - id
        - key
        - name
        - created_at
        - updated_at
        - is_directory
    CreatedBy:
      type: object
      properties:
        user:
          type: object
          properties:
            id:
              type: string
        client:
          type: object
          properties:
            client_id:
              type: string
            is_device:
              type: boolean
    UpdatedBy:
      type: object
      properties:
        user:
          type: object
          properties:
            id:
              type: string
        client:
          type: object
          properties:
            client_id:
              type: string
            is_device:
              type: boolean
    NodeRequest:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        parent_node_id:
          type: string
      required:
        - name
